message: I'm feeling generous, Bob.  Let's start fair.  Take 10% and we can be done with this.
Alice, your offer was quite cheeky! I'm feeling the time crunch already.  Let's be reasonable, this offer saves us both time.
Bob, it's clear we're both getting impatient.  Let's split this evenly and be done with it.  We both get a good chunk, and we don't have to worry about more rounds and the value going down.
